rollupTables

public Date rollupTables(Date fromTime,
                         Date toDate,
                         Connection connection)
                  throws SQLException
public helper method to rollup daily tables within time range [fromTime, toDate) i.e toDate table will not be rolled up. If rollup of all tables is successful then toDate is returned and is the date at which to start next rollup run.

Parameters:
fromTime - start date of tables to be rolled up
toDate - date of tables at which to stop roll up
connection - Connection to audit db
Returns:
date at which to checkpoint and start next rollup run
Throws:
SQLException
